    "For instance, the tool can be connected with users' codebase in GitHub, scans their code to determine the underlying dependencies, and recommends the steps needed to upgrade safely for their codebase.",
    "The tool offers a humanassisted approach to dependency management, helping organizations overcome the challenges of maintaining dependencies in a rapidly evolving ecosystem.",
